# 💡 Founder Recommendation

I think there's one feature that could make your app stand out from many competitors.

## Introduce a "Health Journey" page

Instead of simply listing reports, show the user's progress over time.

Example:

```text
🩸 Your Health Journey

First Report:
12 Jan 2025

Latest Report:
15 Jul 2026

Reports Uploaded:
8

Tests Tracked:
42

Most Improved:
✅ Hemoglobin

Needs Attention:
⚠ Vitamin D

Latest AI Summary:
Your overall blood markers have improved compared with your first report.
```

This gives users a sense of progress and encourages them to keep using the app over the years.

